Class Choices

  • java.lang.Object
    • models.Choices

  • public class Choices
extends java.lang.Object
    Choices class that links descriptions that the user can see and choose. There are some choices available and the latest (old) choice is also saved so that the program knows this. This class also has a numberofchoices variable that tells to the program how many choices that will be shown and selectable.
